EVERMORE CHEMICA said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 39.04% to NT$134,129,000 from NT$220,029,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            134,129          220,029    
YOY%             -39.04%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,018,800        1,221,691   
YOY%             -16.61% 
=================================================================
 